v/news/hindi/yeh-un-dino-ki-bat-hais-ashi-singh-is-a-hottie-in-real-life-a-look-at-her-pictures/pretty/photostory/69045442.cms|title=Ashi Singh's latest pictures prove that the actress is summer ready \u2013 Yeh Un Dino Ki Bat Hai's Ashi Singh is a hottie in real life; a look at her pictures|website=The Times of India|access-date=6 June 2019}}</ref> She was born in [[Agra]]\nand completed her higher education from Kishor Sanghvi College of Commerce & Economics, [[Mumbai]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.iwmbuzz.com/television/photos/yeh-un-dinon-ki-baat-hai-ashi-singhs-transformation-years/2019/07/08|title=Yeh Un Dinon Ki Baat Hai: Ashi Singh\u2019s transformation over the years|last=Team|first=Author: Editorial|date=8 July 2019|website=IWMBuzz|access-date=7 August 2019}}</ref><ref name=\"TimesNowBirth\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.timesnownews.com/entertainment/news/people/photo-gallery/small-screen-actress-ashi-singh-is-just-the-opposite-of-her-reel-character-in-real-life-see-pics/359433|title=Small screen actress Ashi Singh is just the opposite of her reel character in real life|website=Times Now News|access-date=6 June 2019}}</ref> Singh is best known for portraying Naina Agarwal in [[Sony Entertainment Television|Sony TV]]'s ''[[Yeh Un Dinon Ki Baat Hai]]''.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.iwmbuzz.com/television/snippets/ashi-singh-gets-emotional-receiving-special-gift/2019/07/08|title=Ashi Singh gets emotional after receiving a special gift|last=Team|first=Author: Editorial|date=8 July 2019|website=IWMBuzz|access-date=7 August 2019}}</ref> Presently, she is appearing as Iti Rai in [[Star Plus]]'s ''[[Dil Jaise Dhadke... Dhadakne Do]]''.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://m.dailyhunt.in/news/india/english/cinetalkers-epaper-cinetal/ashi+singh-newsid-123786800|title=Ashi Singh \u2013 Cinetalkers|website=Dailyhunt|access-date=7 August 2019}}</ref>\n\n== Career ==\nAshi Singh made her TV debut through the TV show ''Secret Diaries:The Hidden Chapters in 2015''<ref name=\"TimesNowBirth\" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.tellychakkar.com/tv/features/11-unknown-facts-about-yeh-un-dinon-fame-ashi-singh-180203|title=11 Unknown facts about Yeh Un Dinon fame Ashi Singh|last=Team|first=Tellychakkar|website=Tellychakkar.com|access-date=7 August 2019}}</ref> She was also seen in ''[[Gumrah (TV series)|Gumrah]]'' (season 5) and ''[[Crime Patrol (TV series)|Crime Patrol]]'' (Tamasha Mandli)<ref name=\"TimesPhotos\" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.tellychakkar.com/tv/ashi-singh-aka-naina-of-yeh-un-dinon-ki-baat-hai-giving-her-fans-these-goals-190723|title=Ashi Singh aka Naina of Yeh Un Dinon Ki Baat Hai is giving her fans \u2018THESE\u2019 goals!|last=Team|first=Tellychakkar|website=Tellychakkar.com|access-date=7 August 2019}}</ref> She has also acted in ''[[Savdhaan India]]''.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.indiatoday.in/television/photo/yeh-un-dinon-ki-baat-hai-star-ashi-singh-s-glamorous-avatar-will-stun-you-1476277-2019-03-12|title=Yeh Un Dinon Ki Baat Hai star Ashi Singh's glamorous avatar will stun you|website=India Today|access-date=7 August 2019}}</ref> Ashi starred in the Music video ''Zindagi Tujhse Kya Karen Shikvey'' opposite [[Ayesha Takia]] in 2017.<ref name=\"Ashi Singh - IMDb\">{{Cite web|url=http://www.imdb.com/name/nm9235390/bio|title=Ashi Singh|publisher=IMDb|access-date=7 August 2019}}</ref> She did a small role in ''[[Qaidi Band]]'' as the jailer's daughter.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.primevideo.com/detail/Qaidi-Band/0K63N1PZLWDBKH6RI6IEE8FHC9|title=Prime Video: Qaidi Band|website=primevideo.com|access-date=27 November 2019}}</ref>\n\nIn 2017, she was selected to play the lead role in [[SET India]]'s show, ''[[Yeh Un Dinon Ki Baat Hai]]''.  \n\n== Media ==\nSingh was a finalist for BizAsia's TV Personality 2018 award and she was ranked 10 on that list.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.bizasialive.com/harshad-chopda-crowned-tv-personality-2018/|title=Harshad Chopda crowned TV Personality 2018|last=#|date=25 December 2018|website=BizAsia {{!}} Media, Entertainment, Showbiz, Events and Music|access-date=7 August 2019}}</ref> She ranked 18th in Eastern Eye's \"50 Sexiest Asian Women 2018\" list.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.fuzionproductions.com/just-wow-ashi-singh-is-the-highest-placed-newcomer-in-this-popular-list/|title=JUST WOW : Ashi Singh Is The Highest Placed Newcomer in This Popular List!|last=says|first=Smita|date=6 January 2019|website=Fuzion Productions|access-date=7 August 2019}}</ref> In 2019 she has featured in the cover interview of EasternEye in its 1500th issue, in the title of \"The Future Belongs to Ashi Singh\".<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.easterneye.biz/the-future-belongs-to-ashi-singh/|title=The future belongs to Ashi Singh|last=Nazir|first=Asjad|date=29 March 2019|website=EasternEye|access-date=7 August 2019}}</ref>\n\n== Filmography ==\n===Television===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! Year !! Show !! Role !! Channel\n|-\n|2015\n|''Secret Diaries: The Hidden Chapters''\n|Lavanya\n|[[Channel V]]\n|-\n| 2017\u201319\n| ''[[Yeh Un Dinon Ki Baat Hai]]''\n| Naina Agarwal\n| [[Sony Entertainment Television|Sony TV]]\n|}\n2020 dil jasie Dhadke do \n===Movies===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! Year !! Movie !! Role !! Reference\n|-\n| 2017\n| ''[[Qaidi Band]]''\n| Tulika\n|\n|}\n\n== Award and nominations ==\n{{refimprove|section|date=November 2019}}\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! Year !! Award !! Category !! Result\n!References\n|-\n| 2018 || [[Gold Awards]] || Best Debut Female || {{nom}}\n|\n|-\n|rowspan=\"5\"|2019\n| [[Kalakar Awards]] || Best Debut Female || {{Won}} \n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.fuzionproductions.com/kalakar-awards-2019-heres-the-winners-list-in-pics/|title=Kalakar Awards 2019 : Here's The WINNERS List \u2013 IN PICS!|last=Says|first=Suhani|date=21 January 2019|website=Fuzion Productions|access-date=7 August 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Gold A